data.description: VA Assumable loan 2.5% balance $295K! $5000 in Seller Concessions! This spacious 5BR/4BA home features, 2 Living Areas (Bonus room) making it perfect for a growing family or those in need of plenty of space. Primary Room boasts 2 Walk-In closets. Family Room is wired for Surround Sound. One Full Bath Down and 2 rooms upstairs with Full Ensuite Bathrooms and one more Full Bath up. The highlight of this home is the Guest/Mother-in-law Room, conveniently located downstairs for added privacy. Dining Room can serve as Flex Room as Office/Study.  Eat In Kitchen with plenty of room for full Dining Table. With its sizeable layout, you'll have plenty of room to relax and enjoy. One of the exceptional features of this property is its prime location with a backyard that backs up to a golf course and home has extended Patio wired for Hot Tub/Spa. Although Golf Course is inactive you'll have a serene environment to unwind, without neighbors behind you! This home offers a unique setting. Zoned for sought after Schertz-Cibolo-UC School District. Quick access to Randolph AFB (15 min), and to I35 and shopping.  Refrigerator, TV on back Patio and Water Softener convey.  Storm Doors front and back. Don't miss out on the opportunity to own this fantastic property in Fairway Ridge!
